{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Demand financial compensation from the US & Israel for damage to our economy",
        "additional_details": "In our view, America and Israel's war on Iran risks:\r\n \r\n- causing steep increases in the price of food and utilities\r\n- precipitating a UK recession and causing economic hardship for millions\r\n- making foreign travel more expensive or difficult (not least due to a potential shortage of jet fuel)\r\n- increasing Islamophobia and antisemitism by further polarising communities\r\n- increasing the risk of Britain becoming involved in a major global conflict that places our infrastructure and country at risk",
        "background": "The US and Israel attacked Iran while US-Iranian negotiations were ongoing. We believe this war of aggression has had widespread global consequences, increased the cost of fuel, and places our economy, security, and way of life at risk. We require compensation for these effects on our country.",
